text: Georgy de Davydov (born 25 March 1874, date of death unknown) was a Russian sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Russia Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău
